Package org.birchframework.framework.jaxrs

Class Responses

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.birchframework.framework.jaxrs.Responses
  • public class Responses
extends Object
    REST/HTTP response utilities. Enables streamlined interaction with Response objects via functional programming style enabled by Java Lambdas, such as: 

     Responses.of(service.findBookByISBN(anISBN)).ifOKOrElse(
    Book.class,
    book -> log.info("Book: {}", book.toString()),   // book is automatically desrialized as an instance of Book.class
    errorCode -> log.error("Error retrieving book with ISBN: {}; error: {}", anISBN, errorCode.asString())
 );
    This class is not thread-safe. The factory of(Response) must be called for each new Response object.
    Author:
    Keivan Khalichi
